thread.title: BRIEF-Japan Corporate Housing Service to repurchase up to 5.1 pct shares

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Japan Corporate Housing Service to repurchase up to 5.1 pct shares

organizations.name: reuters) - japan corporate housing service inc

text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - Japan Corporate Housing Service Inc
* Says it will repurchase up to 500,000 shares of its common stock, representing 5.1 percent of outstanding, at the price of 897 yen per share, on Feb. 6
* Says share repurchase price at up to 448.5 million yen in total
Source text in Japanese: goo.gl/gtAoCe
